    "Experiment: ant foraging with structured rule-based prompting",
    "The following three variants of the ants foraging simulation were applied:",
    "The original NetLogo model (henceforth simply called \"NetLogo\"). 2.",
    "The model in which the rule-governed ants of the original model are replaced by LLM-governed ants (henceforth called \"LLM\"). 3.",
    "A hybrid model in which half of the ants are rule-governed and the other half are LLM-governed (henceforth called \"Hybrid\")."
